      1793,
      793,
      1881
    ],
    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\n|\\overrightarrow{KP} + \\overrightarrow{KC} + \\overrightarrow{KD}|_{\\min} = 3KG = 3 \\cdot \\frac{5}{2} = \\frac{15}{2}.\n$$"
  },
